    },
    {
      "number": "Question 3",
      "text": "How can we create more opportunities for nuanced discussions about complex topics, given the strong community interest in these areas?",
      "prompt": "Consider: Safe spaces for dialogue, educational programming that explores multiple viewpoints."
    },
    {
      "number": "Question 4",
